snippet.title: Yi Xian: The Cultivation Card Game Coming 2022 | TGS 2022
snippet.description:
Wishlist Now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1948800/Yi_Xian_The_Cultivation_Card_Game/

Yi Xian: The Cultivation Card Game is an online DBG with a background of cultivation. Every game is a deck building from scratch. Players can have stronger decks by changing cards, and then build more powerful routines to defeat all opponents to win.

Launch in 2022 Q4
